theorem Topology.closure_boundary_eq_boundary {X : Type*} [TopologicalSpace X] {A : Set X} :
    closure (closure (A : Set X) \ interior A) = closure A \ interior A := by
  have h_closed : IsClosed (closure (A : Set X) \ interior A) :=
    Topology.isClosed_closure_diff_interior (A := A)
  simpa [h_closed.closure_eq]

theorem Topology.closureFrontier_eq_self
    {X : Type*} [TopologicalSpace X] (A : Set X) :
    closure (frontier A) = frontier A := by
  have h_closed : IsClosed (frontier A) := isClosed_frontier
  simpa using h_closed.closure_eq
